  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45584</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_004_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたし……わたしのせいで……虹輪が……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's...it's all my fault... the Prism Ring...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45732</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_004_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>まだ原因もわかんねーんだろ、気にすんなって。
だいじょーぶだって……タンス野郎もなんか言えよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We still ain't sure about a thing. Cheer up! Everything‘ll work out! Piece of wood, say something for once!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45836</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_004_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>気にすることないだーよ。&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;は悪くないだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Don't worry, &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt;. You aren't evil at all.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45916</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_004_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうそう、悪くない悪くない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>See! Not evil! Not evil at all!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46016</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_004_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>今回の件で一番悪いのは、このクソぼうずだーよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>For this time the worst one here is the damned kiddo here.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46096</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_004_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうそう、オレが全部悪い……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yep, yep! I'm completely terrible, ain't I...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46184</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_004_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んだよ！　なんでオレが悪いんだよ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The hell I am! Why am I the bad one now!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46348</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_004_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おめぇがかっこつけて、魔物を退治しようとしたからだ。
放っておけば、&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;もこんな目に合わなかっただよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let me say it nicely. YOU were supposed to exterminate the monsters that appeared but left the job unfinished so &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt; had to use magic and experience a bad moment!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46432</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_004_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あんな状況放っておけねーだろ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's just how things happened, damn it!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46584</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_004_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>けっ！　ヒーロー気取りがぁ！　おめぇのかっこつけで、
&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;まで巻きこまれてかわいそーだど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hah! Admit it! The "Hero" title got over your head! Because you tried to act all cool &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt; got involved in all of this!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46656</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_004_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オ、オレかぁ……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...It was all because of me...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
